We’re excited to share our company profile for your review.
It’s our pleasure to introduce Boomaa Consultants as one of India’s leading
recruitment firms. We take pride in delivering high-quality staffing
solutions and managing all HR-related needs with efficiency,
professionalism, and a strong commitment to service.
Our team is equipped to source exceptional talent from across India,
supported by experienced recruiters and headhunters who understand the
importance of accuracy, integrity, and timely delivery.
We serve a wide range of industries, including:
FMCG, Healthcare, BPO, ITES, IT, Hospitality, Retail, Manufacturing,
Telecom, Banking, Mutual Funds, Insurance, NBFC, Construction & Real

To: <grievance-officer@pharmeasy.in>


Dear Grievance Officer,

Ticket id for your reference: 22204469

I am writing on behalf of Indoco Remedies Ltd., the rightful owner of the registered trademark "Triz" (Trademark No. 619555), to follow up on a formal infringement complaint that was sent to your team on 19 November 2025 at 7:10 PM and follow up on 26 November 2025 at 6:11 PM.
We submitted all required documents, including the Trademark Certificates and the Brand Authorization Letter. However, no action has been taken regarding the reported infringing product listings.

Details of Earlier Complaint

Infringing URLs:
https://pharmeasy.in/online-medicine-order/m-triz-strip-of-10-tablets-3489146

Register Trademark: Triz
Original URLs:
https://www.apollopharmacy.in/medicine/triz-syrup-60ml
https://www.truemeds.in/medicine/triz-5-mg-syrup-60-ml-tm-syup1-004167
https://www.truemeds.in/medicine/triz-10-mg-tablet-10-tm-tacr1-041354
The unauthorized use of our registered trademark “Triz” in the infringing listings constitutes a clear violation of our intellectual property rights and is likely to mislead consumers.  

Legal Obligation Under Indian Law

As per the Information Technology (Intermediary Guidelines and Digital Media Ethics Code) Rules, 2021, particularly Rule 3(1)(D) and Rule 3(1)(G), intermediaries are required to:
  • Acknowledge and act upon complaints relating to violation of intellectual property rights within 72 hours of receiving such notice.
  • Remove or disable access to infringing content to retain safe harbour protection under Section 79 of the Information Technology Act, 2000.
Failure to take timely action places the intermediary at risk of losing its safe harbour protection, exposing it to legal liability for continued infringement.

Requested Action

We hereby request the following, on priority:
  1. Immediate removal of all infringing listings mentioned above.
  2. Confirmation of action taken along with timelines.
  3. Steps being implemented to prevent recurrence of such trademark infringement on your platform.
All relevant documentation has already been shared. Should you require additional information, feel free to reach out to us.

We trust that your office will handle this matter with urgency as mandated by law.
Awaiting your prompt response and compliance confirmation.
Warm regards,
Apurva

Thank you.

Regards,
Mayur Kachare

Hello Srikanth,

Greetings from PharmEasy!

This email is with regards to your order # 655242665375825920-68659, as checked your order was canceled on 06 December 2025. Due to some unforeseen circumstances, the order was not delivered to you by the expected date of delivery. We apologize for the inconvenience caused to you with your order.

As a token of apology, we have already credited Rs.30/- to your PharmEasy wallet.Also we would like to inform you that cancellation refund of Rs 604.58 /- initiated on 06 December 2025. The refund  will refunded  payments source within 05-07 business days.

We would request you to place a new order and we will ensure the order is delivered to you on priority.

Be rest assured as  we have jotted down the details of your experience and PharmEasy will ensure all appropriate actions are taken to prevent similar situations from happening in the future. Looking forward to delighting you soon.

For any further assistance, please reopen this ticket or reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section.

PharmEasy
